| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2025-5659 — Recovery Inhibition (medusa)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 71fa3c36-8c1c-5414-9579-1f3ba7dbf5e6"
index=* sourcetype=endpoint*
| where (CommandLine="*recoveryenabled no*" OR CommandLine="*bootstatuspolicy ignoreallfailures*") AND (process="*\bcdedit.exe")
